title: The World Owes You Nothing
itunes:title: The World Owes You Nothing
description:
Ep. 119 - Everything is immediate nowadays. You can get the answer to almost any question, anywhere, and at the touch of your smartphone. Because of that, people today want immediate gratification. Success is never immediate, success takes time. In fact, it can take years. In this episode I talk about how to get to where you want by playing the long game and concentrating on improving with every failure.
